13a53bd3-0448-43d9-9c86-4003fc309276.title: Diablo
13a53bd3-0448-43d9-9c86-4003fc309276.summary: Diablo II is an action RPG where players battle through dark fantasy realms, facing demonic hordes and powerful bosses. With deep lore, character customization, and cooperative gameplay, it remains a classic in the genre.

d0874cd7-8805-48f0-a61f-fcec285debdf.title: World of Warcraft
d0874cd7-8805-48f0-a61f-fcec285debdf.summary: World of Warcraft is a massively multiplayer online role-playing game set in the expansive fantasy world of Azeroth. Players create characters, embark on epic quests, engage in player-vs-player combat, and join guilds in a persistent online universe.
